application_type_full: Outline planning permission: Some matters reserved
decision_conditions:
Prior to the commencement of any phase of the development adjoining the waterway, full details of any proposed lighting and CCTV scheme shall be submitted to and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority, in consultation with British Waterways.  The approved lighting and CCTV scheme should be implemented prior to first occupation of the relevant part of the development. 

REASON: In the interest of crime prevention, ecology, visual amenity and the canal setting.
